Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  第一  我腿没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, first, my leg is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二  外勤工作还用你教\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And second, what's with the tips on field work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁死了轮到你扮芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who died and made you Finch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时得扮上  等着真身回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's the role I gotta play until the real one comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么时候  这都超过一星期了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And when is that? It's been over a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没电话  没短信  连个求救信号都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No...call, no--no text. Not even a smoke signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇准备好了就会联系我们  在此之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Finch will reach out to us when he's good and ready. Until then--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高兴见到你  约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nice to see you, too, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是从哪儿冒出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where the hell did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近在[德州]厄尔巴索\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}El paso, most recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒品战之类的事儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The thing with the narco-trafficker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然相关  不过不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Very relevant, but not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧下街角吧你们俩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Take a peek around that corner, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埋伏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁要来搅局啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who are the party crashers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛的杀手  在等你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima trigger teams... waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手上至少有六把冲锋枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}with no less than six submachine guns
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一把原装的俄罗斯7型火箭推进榴弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and one honest-to-goodness Russian RPG-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得马上隐形\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need to get invisible fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话和耳机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Phones and earpieces now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街上不安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Streets aren't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛的机器上线了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima's machine is online.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在纽约五区范围内随时随地监视我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can see us anywhere and everywhere in the five boroughs of New York city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"  你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan? You confirmed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的名字首当其冲  格里尔资源在手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Our names are on the list, and Greer is keeping score.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的系统  摄像头  电话  车载定位系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All systems--cameras, phones, the GPS in your car
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能追踪到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}can track us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  "撒马利亚人"现在能自我思考\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So what, Samaritan can think for itself now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-自我学习了吗  -应该不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- It can learn? - I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  它还只能监视和跟踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Right now, all it can do is watch us and follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但记住  我们的机器能看到的  "撒马利亚人"都能看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just remember--what our machine sees, Samaritan sees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个上帝同桌玩牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Two Gods playing with the same deck of cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得另寻出路\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need to find another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(191,129)\bord0\shad0\fn方正综艺_GBK\c&HC8C9BC&\fs0\fsp1}信号不可用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里尔先生  我还以为你系统的试运行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Greer, I'd assumed the beta test of your system
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会更加\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}would be a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专业\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意式咖啡机随后就到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The espresso machine is on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以向你保证  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I can assure you, Senator,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"运作精准  如瑞士手表\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan is running as smooth as a Swiss watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How long will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经获取全市监控信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've had all the city's domain awareness feeds
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四个小时了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}for four hours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这四个小时的成就吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And look at what those four hours have already produced.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约市所有的恐怖疑犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All probable terrorists in the city of New York
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已被实时定位仪定位  分类  并追踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}pinpointed, categorized, and tracked with an up-to-the-second GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以向你保证  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can assure you, Senator,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很快就能为你找到一个硬目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that we will have a hard target for you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到之后会通知我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you'll inform me when you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一时间通知你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You will be the first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们已经有数十个结果了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know we've gotten dozens of results already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们全都已经打包待赠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Any one of these guys is practically gift-wrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会赠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And we'll deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是必须先找出哈罗德・芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But not until after we've located Harold Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进展如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where are we on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"找不到线索  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan couldn't find a lead, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能离城了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He may have skipped town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不是应该调用更高级\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Should we consider turning on its higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更有认知力的功能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}more cognitive functions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西有思维  为什么不用呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This thing has a mind. Why don't we use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因很简单  我们缺少硬件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}For the simple reason we don't have the hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然找不到芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If it can't find this Finch,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二等奖如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}how 'bout the next best thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们让它整合哈罗德・芬奇的所有资料\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If we have it combine everything it knows about Harold Finch
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它找出和他关系最近的联系人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and ask it to find his closest living connection,
