Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad1\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\c&H0500DB&\fs10\frz1.034\4c&H9A9AB2&\move(252.2,99.033,263.5,101,153,195)}可能目标 尝试识别中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad1\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\c&H0500DB&\fs10\frz1.034\4c&H9A9AB2&\move(263.474,104.387,266.6,105,271,312)}可能目标 尝试识别中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贴墙走  上面有摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hug the wall. There's a camera up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用23大街上的弗来勋线轻轨掩护我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're covered on 23rd street by the flushing line elevated tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们冲过去  应该就不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We make it that far, and maybe we don't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个街区外的六名德西玛特工杀掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}get shot by the six Decima agents waiting a block away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"入门教程\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's go.
