Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里等着交通灯变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hold here until the light changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄像头角度会根据交通状态转换\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The camera angle switches with oncoming traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等交通灯再变  我们就完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}When that light switches, we're screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在管不了无关号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We can't worry about irrelevant numbers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在想什么  让我们低调点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What is it thinking... telling us to lay low
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又给我们新号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}then handing us a new number?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是生命  芬奇会要我们去拯救\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is a life, and Finch would tell us to save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你那神秘莫测的老大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So you tell your complicated boss
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它不想我有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}if it wants me to step out of danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就别光给我号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}then I need more than just numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I want a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  她给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Fine. She's giving it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我路上告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll tell you on--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Oh, no. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(230.977,88)\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\c&H060606&\fs8}搜寻  {\c&H3400D2&\b1\shad1}哈罗德・芬奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(208.217,104)\fad(0,50)\bord0\shad0\b1\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\c&HC2E8CF&\fs6}主要目标未找到  寻找相关联系人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(20,0)\bord0\shad1\b1\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\c&H330EEE&\fs9\pos(243.454,107.5)\4c&H7068C0&}找到相关联系人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\b1\shad0\fn微软雅黑\fs6\c&H92B39C&\K17\pos(194.603,95)}分析完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来"撒马利亚人"找到联系人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Looks like Samaritan's found a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是家人  朋友  同事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Could be family, a friend, a coworker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她带过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Bring her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(20,0)\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\c&H2E00D2&\fs7\pos(193.802,167.019)}亨德里克斯  格蕾斯・R
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们心里不要忧愁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"Let not your hearts be troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}此段选自《圣经・新约・约翰福音・第14章》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我父的家里有许多住处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"In my father's house are many rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我若去为你们预备了地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"And if I go to prepare a place for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"I will come again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在哪里  叫你们也在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And where I am, you may be also."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正宋三_GBK\c&H8B8B75&\fs12\frz357.2\pos(233.043,182.007)}哈罗德・紫崖燕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说  我会说说死者的事  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ordinarily, I'd say a few words about the deceased, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  没关系  神父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, that's all right, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was lovely. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸案太不幸了  一下子夺走这么多性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The bombing was such a tragedy. So many lives taken at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽不认识你未婚夫  但愿他安息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I didn't know your fiance, but I pray his soul finds peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是想  至少有一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I would have thought at least one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有很多  他并没有家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not a crowd--he didn't really have any family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有位朋友  或者  同事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but a friend or... a coworker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个人  从心底珍惜哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}one other person who knew how truly special Harold was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想来道别\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and wanted to say good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨德里克斯女士  您叫了车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ms. Hendricks, you ordered a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  去肯尼迪机场\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yes! To JFK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我帮您拿吧  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Let me get that. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国际航站楼是吧  您去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}International, right? Where you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去意大利面试\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm going to a job interview in Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道自己想不想去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm not even sure if I want it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我得给他们展示下我的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but I have to show them my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦小心轻放\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If you could be really careful with this--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是油画\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Those are paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是艺术家啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're an artist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女儿喜欢画画\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My daughter loves to paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有网站吗  我给她看看您的作品\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you have a website? I'd love to show her your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真好  我应该有带名片\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's sweet. Yeah, I think I have a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She'll be so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您真好心\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nice of you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在打流感疫苗晚了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Little late for the flu shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨德里克斯女士  我是斯蒂尔斯警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ms. Hendricks, I'm Detective Stills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以前见过  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We met before. Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是哪儿来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搭档和我得把你送到安全的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My partner and I need to get you to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此人效力于一个极端危险的犯罪组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This man works for a very dangerous criminal organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人马上就到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and others are on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们得快走  重点是快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So we need to hurry. Emphasis on the hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨德里克斯女士公寓楼下截取到图像\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Image captures from down the street from Ms. Hendricks' apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的人得手前被放倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Our operative was intercepted before he could acquire her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对救他们的这两位应该很熟悉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I believe you're familiar with the two who came to her rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们目前正在曼哈顿追踪他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're currently tracking them across Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏玩够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Enough of these games.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎卡里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Zachary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有人都派出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Deploy all operatives into the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把格蕾斯・亨德里克斯带过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Bring me Grace Hendricks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除掉其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and eliminate the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  你干什么  你们不能来这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, no, no. What are you doing? You can't be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能啊  莱奈尔  我们是警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yes, we can, Lionel. We're police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯蒂尔斯警探  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Detective Stills, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你玩死我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're killing me with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这儿不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's not safe for you in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有办法关掉那些玩意儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Any way to turn those things off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄像头么  现在局里到处都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The cameras? Department's got 'em up all over the place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱奈尔  这是格蕾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Lionel, meet Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些很坏的坏蛋想伤害她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's got some very bad people trying to hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这两位警探救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but these detectives saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  他们可擅长了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah. They're good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给她找个休息的地方吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now can we find her a place to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, all right, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体人员  就位\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All units, take positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我们已经包围了警局\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sir, we have the precinct surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以进入\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're ready to move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hold your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的情况  可能需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The situation may require a certain amount of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智取\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}finesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不咋地  好歹是热的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's lousy, but it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么有人想伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why would someone want to hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can't tell you what's going on out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在这儿你很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But in here, you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两位警探  斯蒂尔斯和他搭档\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The other detectives-- Stills and his partner--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一直这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are they always like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们确实看着是有点愣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I know they come off a little stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他们救过我很多次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But they've saved my life dozens of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  他们是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Trust me-- they're the good guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  有什么能效劳的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sorry. Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅班克特工\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Special Agent Maybank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有个名叫亨德里克斯的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's a woman by the name of Hendricks here.
