Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有逮捕令\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I have a warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式授权的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's notarized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这花招挺漂亮  但对姐没用\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's a cute trick, but you ain't getting anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题吗  警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is there a problem, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-弗斯科警督  -梅班克特工\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Lieutenant Fusco. - Special Agent Maybank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正准备讯问那嫌疑人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We were just about to question your suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就感觉她背后有大案\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I had a feeling she was tied to something bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意的话  我带她到审讯室见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now, if you like, I can bring her to you in the interrogation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有劳了  -好  这边请\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Please. - Sure. Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-稍等下  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- It'll just be a second. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-晚安  警司  -晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Good night, Sarge. - Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗斯科\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Fusco.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓了个夜游神\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got a late-night collar here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着两把未注册的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Picked her up with two unregistered weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想打扰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hate to crash the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有位朋友认为我可以帮上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but a mutual friend thought I could help in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就让自己被逮捕吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So you got yourself arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是第一次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wouldn't be the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我解开吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Help me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在779B证物箱里  有一卷铜线\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In evidence locker 7-7-9-B, there's a coil of copper wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在443A里  有一副尖嘴钳\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In 4-4-3-A, there's a pair of needle-nosed pliers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要它们  还有一盘胶带和一根延长电线\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I need them, a roll of duct tape, and an extension cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这点儿吗  甜心宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is that all, Cocoa Puffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们的人部署在警察局周围\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tell our men to position themselves around the station
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监控没有覆盖的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}where there's no surveillance coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题吗  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is there a problem, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不是唯一耳目遍布的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're not the only ones with eyes and ears everywhere.
