Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯蒂尔斯警探怎么可能是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How is Detective Stills one of the good guys
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他根本就不是斯蒂尔斯警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}when he's not even Detective Stills?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨德里克斯  格蕾斯・R\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hendricks, Grace R.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗德岛设计学院美术学士  耶鲁美术硕士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}BFA, Rhode Island School of Design, MFA, Yale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're a smart lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以听着你走出那扇门会有什么下场\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So listen to what happens when you walk out that door.
