Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不就是被某个名叫扎卡里的蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you'll be grabbed by some lummox named Zachary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓进一辆挂着假俄亥俄牌照的越野车里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in an SUV with bogus Ohio plates--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可绝对惨过你待在这间房里被谎言保护着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}a fate far worse than the lies told to protect you in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信由你  她也是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Believe it or not, she's one of the good guys too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不敢相信这里真是警察局了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I barely believe this is a police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的形势  你无法掌控\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're in a situation you can't control
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远超出你的想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that's larger than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖坐着  我们会保住你的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sit tight, and we'll keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱奈尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Lionel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我找到什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}what did you find for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么玩意儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感应线圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}An induction coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是局里的电信箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is the precinct's telecom box.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有摄像头的线都要穿过这堵墙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The wires from all the cameras run through this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一条线都被铜包皮保护着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Each of those wires is protected by a copper sheath
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用110伏电压让它们过载\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}which I'm overloading with 110 volts of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛  你打算烧掉这地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What, are you trying to burn the place down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,略烤一下下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just cooking it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快把这些处理掉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're gonna want to dispose of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明早你们IT部门的人可要上班了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Especially when your I.T. guys show up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了  还有别的需要吗  公主殿下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Terrific. Anything else, princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手机和一辆便衣警车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your phone and an unmarked car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  别是往中国打长途\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Here. You better not be calling China.
