Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没想到我居然会喜欢新泽西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Never thought I'd love the sight of New Jersey.
