Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切安全  除了咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}From everything but the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们脱离监控了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And, yes, we're off the radar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在五区之外就没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}as long as we're outside the five boroughs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"监视不了这么远  暂时还不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan can't see this far...yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得回去找格蕾斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We have to go back and find Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛倾尽一切对付我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If Decima's throwing everything they have at us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定是要利用她找芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}then she's their way to get to Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还当忠诚的守望者呢  哈罗德都离开你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Still the faithful watchdog, huh? Even after Harold left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底帮不帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are you gonna help us or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就怕你不问呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I thought you'd never ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到红色的区域没\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}See everything in red?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是市里的死角\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}These are dead zones in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些地方我们的机器找不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Spots where our machine can't find a hint
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音频和视频监视\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of audio or visual surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛抓走格蕾斯时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}When Decima took Grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们消失在了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}they disappeared to this spot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红钩航运码头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Red Hook Marine Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个码头都没有被监视\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}An entire port blacked out to surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人不想世界看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Someone doesn't want the world to see
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里进出的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}what's going in or coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的薄饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Here's your pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看这是最可能找到格蕾丝的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm guessing it's our best shot at finding Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们去看看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  运动爱好者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Stop the clock, sports fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩打算怎么回城\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How do either of you plan on getting us back into the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\i1\c&H211017&\fs30\3c&H5D6D83&\pos(140.992,104.786)}急运送货服务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的车来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's our ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是在哪儿  该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where am I, damn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你问题呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I asked you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  我这是在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tell me where I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿没什么关系  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where you are is of very little interest, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁  这个问题比较值得追寻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who you are--now, that's a question worth pursuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What right do you have
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑架我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to abduct me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囚禁我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to keep me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的问题只会拖延我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your questions only delay my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now, tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾斯・亨德里克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Grace Hendricks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以摘掉帽子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You can lose the hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个区域都是死角  就是说没有摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Whole area's a dead zone, meaning "camera free."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我们丢掉了手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And since we ditched our phones,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才在八局时顺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I took the liberty of grabbing a few of these
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个这玩意儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}on our way out of the 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  有多少坏蛋要处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, so how many bad guys are we looking at here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火力如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What kind of firepower?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这片区域  只能两眼一抹黑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As long as we're here, we're flying blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用回经典老招了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}a chance for some good old-fashioned recon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只有雇员信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's nothing here but employee records.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她应该在码头的四个集装箱货船里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's gotta be on one of those four container ships at dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定是看到了四艘船吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're sure you saw four ships out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,码头载货单只标注了三艘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Terminal manifest only lists three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去后边看看那第四艘如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What do you say we take a look behind door Number Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩下去甲板找格蕾丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You two head below deck, try to find Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去上面看着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll keep watch up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看到格蕾丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No sign of Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看到任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大的船需要很多船员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Takes a big crew to run a ship this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人都去哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴唇  指甲变色\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Discoloration of the lips, fingernails.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸骤停\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Signs of respiratory arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是  肉毒杆菌毒素\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm guessing... botulinum toxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作圆满\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}For a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为什么要毒死船员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But why would they poison the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是想隐藏什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Unless they have something to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You guys might wanna come up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西给你们看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's something you should see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电脑服务器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Computer servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个集装箱里约有六十个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd say there's about 60 per container.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.67,0:23:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  都是最尖端的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And, yes... they're state-of-the-art.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种晶片组和加速技术\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}With chipsets and acceleration technology
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我前所未见\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}unlike anything I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你三次机会猜德西玛拿这些干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Three guesses what Decima's gonna use them for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.16,0:23:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用三次也猜得出\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you won't need three.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"吗  但它已经上线了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan? But it's already online.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得它现在就很恐怖吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You think it's scary now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"是全新的系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan's a brand-new system,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在学爬的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}a child learning to crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些服务器  能让它跑起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}These servers... are for when it can run.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死人没法审问\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can't question a dead guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可能还有点用\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But maybe this can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能往高处瞄一点点么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You couldn't have aimed 2 inches higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今儿个人人都吹毛求疵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Everybody's a critic today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你找台电脑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's just go find you a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ready when you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:23:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是德西玛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was Decima, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来盘点库存货物的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Here to take inventory of the cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接收指令的短信都是自动删除的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And receiving orders via self-deleting texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.35,0:24:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们真是从不放水啊  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They never make it easy, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短信无法读取\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can't read the texts,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但机器找到了短信来源\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but the machine found where they came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.11,0:24:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁克林的一幢建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A building in Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是德西玛在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If Decima's camped out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾丝多半也在  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}then Grace probably is too. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫我待在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's telling me to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的交给你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You guys can handle it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢配什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How do you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.83,0:24:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果渴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If you get parched...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.70,0:24:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.52,0:24:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们重新  再来一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's go over it... one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一遍我是插画家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The part where I tell you I'm an illustrator
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.32,0:24:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道在这儿是干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}who has no idea what she's doing here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:24:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是再来一遍你不相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or the part where you don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.62,0:24:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你是插画家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I believe you're an illustrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.43,0:25:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还相信你出生于\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I believe that you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.93,0:25:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1969年4月12日  南卡罗来纳州哥伦比亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}on the 12th of April, 1969, in Columbia, South Carolina,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.71,0:25:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母是保罗・亨德里克斯和玛丽莲・亨德里克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to Paul and Marilyn Hendricks
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.65,0:25:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在森林街一幢浅蓝色的房子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of the pale blue house on Forrester Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.13,0:25:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的卧室在楼上右手边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your bedroom was the upper right one
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.31,0:25:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到街景\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}overlooking the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父母还住在那里  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your parents still live there, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.71,0:25:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的一对儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Charming couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.63,0:25:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.46,0:25:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你学过艺术史\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've studied history of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.27,0:25:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当我是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just think of me as...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.95,0:25:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西斯廷教堂的米开朗基罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Michelangelo in the Sistine Chapel
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.22,0:25:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰天躺着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}lying on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.26,0:25:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要绘出那位看不见摸不到的肖像\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}trying to paint a portrait of a rather elusive subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.71,0:25:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米开朗基罗是站着画的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Michelangelo painted it standing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.99,0:25:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艺术史里学到的小东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}One of those little things you learn in art history.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.95,0:25:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没法帮你画出上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I can't help you make a picture of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.05,0:25:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.58,0:25:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你结过婚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ever been married?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.30,0:25:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你手中的资料会告诉你我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sure that file of yours can tell you the answer's no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫁给了你的事业吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Married to your career then?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.26,0:26:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想了解下你的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm simply trying to get a sense of your life
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.02,0:26:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你生活中的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and the people in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.77,0:26:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  爸爸  没别人了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mom, Dad... no one else?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.34,0:26:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了  就朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nobody. Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.64,0:26:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多是艺术家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mostly artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.18,0:26:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可惜啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Seems a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.34,0:26:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如此美丽  智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}woman of your beauty, intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.75,0:26:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才华横溢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}obvious talent--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.40,0:26:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你会很受欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd think you'd be quite a catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.72,0:26:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我四年前订过婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was engaged once, four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.20,0:26:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But he's dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.11,0:26:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.44,0:26:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.81,0:26:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,港口炸弹袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The ferry bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.70,0:26:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}His name was Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.80,0:26:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲剧啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.86,0:26:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我讲讲哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Please... tell me about Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.78,0:27:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在恐怖袭击中失去挚爱一定很痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Must be awful losing a loved one to an act of terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.53,0:27:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿他的葬礼能让你有所解脱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I hope his burial provided you with a modicum of closure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.16,0:27:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是悼念会  不是葬礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was a memorial, not a burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.38,0:27:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的遗骸消失在海里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}His remains were lost at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.59,0:27:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的解脱跟你无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And my closure's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.11,0:27:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能说出一件关于哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can you name any one thing about Harold
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.31,0:27:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定绝对真实的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that you know to be absolutely true?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.57,0:27:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能说出几十件  他善良  智慧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can name dozens. He was kind, intelligent--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.13,0:27:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.63,0:27:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德・紫崖燕  自由软件工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Harold Martin, freelance software engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.27,0:27:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母双亡  热爱艺术  道德高尚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Orphan with a love of art and a heart of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.45,0:27:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这么说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.49,0:27:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是这么告诉你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So he told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.71,0:27:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在暗示哈罗德骗了我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are you implying that Harold lied to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.41,0:27:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在暗示你的哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm implying that your Harold
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.00,0:27:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着隐姓埋名的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}lived a remarkably anonymous life...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.80,0:27:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许不只一个身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps more than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.36,0:27:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.49,0:27:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.68,0:28:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想辨别出\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm simply trying to discern
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.21,0:28:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于他的事  你是在骗我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}whether you're lying to me about this man
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.61,0:28:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是在骗自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or just to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.37,0:28:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't know who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.19,0:28:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是要怎样  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or how this ends, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.19,0:28:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止  别再提问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're done here. No more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.37,0:28:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再提我  我的生活  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No more questions about me and my life or harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.32,0:28:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要发脾气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No need to lose your temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.89,0:28:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于我你只需要知道这些  老家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Here's all you need to know about me, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.21,0:28:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸酗酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My dad was an alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.52,0:28:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎把家搞散\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nearly tore the family to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.33,0:28:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成长于那样的家庭里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The thing about growing up that way--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.85,0:28:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会精通于看穿谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you get good at spotting lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.35,0:28:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精通到开始从所有人身上寻找谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So good that you start expecting them from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.00,0:28:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如何确定哈罗德告诉我的  是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So how do I know what Harold told me was true?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.84,0:28:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他一出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Because when he came along,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.69,0:28:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就违背了自己的本能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}against every instinct,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.01,0:28:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信任他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I gave him my trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.07,0:28:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Somehow I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.98,0:28:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他永远不会辜负我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}he would never break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.65,0:29:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你对此有一丝一毫的怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And if you doubt that even for a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.82,0:29:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你在骗自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you're the one who's lying to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.52,0:29:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你深爱着他  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You truly loved him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.32,0:29:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意不惜一切来拯救他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I would have done anything to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.05,0:29:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德同样不惜为我做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And Harold would have done anything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.27,0:29:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.05,0:29:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对此深信不疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I have no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.40,0:29:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Answer me one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.22,0:29:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么对哈罗德这么感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why are you so interested in Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.51,0:29:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.99,0:29:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的茶凉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your tea's gone cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.37,0:29:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再添点热的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Feel free to freshen it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.57,0:29:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎卡里  我和目标的谈话结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Zachary, I finished our interview with our subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.29,0:29:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到她的保护者了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have you found her protectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.87,0:30:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  先生  "撒马利亚人"定位了他们的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yes, sir. Samaritan has located their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.77,0:30:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're moving in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.99,0:30:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.23,0:30:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.85,0:30:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.21,0:30:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么弄到这车的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How did you get this vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.36,0:30:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  老兄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Easy, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.91,0:30:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只讨要一块钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I-I just asked for a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.64,0:30:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就给了我车钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They gave me the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.14,0:30:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我们跟丢他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sir, we lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.06,0:30:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们调虎离山了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They engineered a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.56,0:30:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们为什么要调虎离山\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now, why would they create a distraction
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.73,0:30:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们引到城市的一边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that dragged us all the way to one side of the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.71,0:30:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非他们正在赶去另一边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}unless they were on their way to the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.80,0:30:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的位置暴露了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Our location has been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.58,0:30:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拆卸所有设备  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Disassemble everything. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.12,0:30:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要再躲各种能看的超级计算机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Next time we need to hide from an all-seeing super computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.48,0:30:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分开坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we're getting separate trunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢纽约出租车司机的特点就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My favorite thing about New York cabbies--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.59,0:31:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们记性不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}they have terrible memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.51,0:31:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到没\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.44,0:31:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经忘记我们了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You forgot us already?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛就躲在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima's holed up in there somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.24,0:31:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的话  格蕾丝也在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and if we're lucky, so is Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.91,0:31:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够躲躲藏藏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sick of hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.80,0:31:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大干一场吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's make some noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.11,0:31:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人叫技术支持吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Somebody call tech support?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.51,0:31:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到一个  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got this one, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.22,0:31:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到格蕾丝了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You find Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.27,0:31:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了一间审讯室  放着两杯茶\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Found an interrogation room set up with tea for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.88,0:31:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是温的  刚错过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Still warm. We just missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.26,0:31:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位朋友会告诉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Our friend here is gonna tell us
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.60,0:31:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对格蕾丝和"撒马利亚人"所知的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}everything he knows about Grace and Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.69,0:31:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深表怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I sincerely doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.64,0:31:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说  你们只需要知道亨德里克斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Besides...all you need to know about Ms. Hendricks is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.23,0:31:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我手里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that she's with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.12,0:31:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时来说  她很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And for the moment, quite safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.24,0:32:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放她走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.07,0:32:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则这位极客就要吃枪子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or geek squad here catches a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.31,0:32:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戏很精彩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Amusing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.24,0:32:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但恐怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.96,0:32:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维吉尔已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Virgil's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.56,0:32:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对  维吉尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Aren't you, virgil?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.43,0:32:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天一亮  格蕾丝・亨德里克斯会出现在杰弗逊大桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}At dawn, Grace Hendricks will be at the Jefferson Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.47,0:32:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很乐意把她还给你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll be very happy to return her to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.04,0:32:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要拿哈罗德・芬奇来换\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in exchange for Harold Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么认为我们会同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What makes you think we'd agree to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.16,0:32:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你同不同意无关紧要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your agreement is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.46,0:32:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传信给芬奇先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get the message to Mr. Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.88,0:32:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他会合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I expect he'll cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.72,0:32:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为亨德里克斯女士着想  别迟到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}For Ms. Hendricks' sake, don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.08,0:32:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能拿哈罗德去换  我们都找不到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We can't trade Harold. We can't even find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.92,0:32:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们只剩数小时时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then we've only got a few hours
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.33,0:32:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想方案营救格蕾丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to come up with a way to save Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.54,0:33:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-喂  -你们好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Yep. - Hi, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.29,0:33:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器说格蕾丝住处的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The machine says the security camera
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.00,0:33:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监控摄像头刚刚失灵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}overlooking the entrance to Grace's building just went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.57,0:33:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们应该会想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thought you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.77,0:33:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正综艺_GBK\c&HBABDBB&\fs17\fsp1\pos(191,129)}信号丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.58,0:33:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.62,0:33:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么关掉摄像头的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How did you take out the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.58,0:33:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还留着几手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I still have a few tricks left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.29,0:33:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本希望还不晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd hoped maybe it wasn't too late,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.80,0:33:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能及时提醒她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that I could warn her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.33,0:33:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想要我  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They want me, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.24,0:33:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会把你交给德西玛  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're not giving you to Decima, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.29,0:33:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才找回你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We just got you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.30,0:34:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个人总能想出办法来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The three of us will come up with some kind of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.02,0:34:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  计划变更可能会让格蕾丝有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, any change of plans would put Grace at risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.10,0:34:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.63,0:34:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去交换她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll trade myself for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.78,0:34:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩和我一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The two of you will stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.02,0:34:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保证德西玛履行承诺  明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and make sure that Decima holds up their end of the deal. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.41,0:34:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都听你的  芬奇  我们会在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Whatever you want, Finch. We'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.53,0:34:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.46,0:34:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.19,0:34:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能尽可能避免暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd like you to avoid violence if at all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.89,0:34:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.81,0:34:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们伤了格蕾丝一根汗毛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}if they harm Grace in any way...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.68,0:34:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全杀掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.17,0:35:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你们仨想出来的最佳方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is the best plan you three could come up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.54,0:35:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们别无选择  莱奈尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We had no choice, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.37,0:35:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不喜欢  我们太暴露\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't like it. We're too exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.08,0:35:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都有摄像头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And there are cameras everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.67,0:35:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们不动手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}which is why we do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.34,0:35:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到万不得已  谁都不会开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No one fires a shot unless we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.46,0:35:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't do this, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.85,0:35:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会想出办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.42,0:35:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们经历过更糟的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We've faced worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.01,0:35:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更糟  有吗  我不觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Worse? Have we? I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.70,0:35:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器上线的那天起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}From the day the machine went online,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.20,0:35:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我潜意识里就知道  自己永远无法摆脱它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}part of me knew that I would never be able to sever myself from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.98,0:36:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有我在乎的人  都有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And that anyone I ever cared about was in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.90,0:36:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝相信这点是自欺欺人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was foolish to imagine otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.41,0:36:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护自己  隐姓埋名\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I tried to guard myself, stay hidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.95,0:36:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开政府  当局  各方人士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}from the government, the authorities, people looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.28,0:36:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是到了这一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Here we still are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.57,0:36:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻无法避免\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This moment was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.82,0:36:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一刻始终在路上等我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This moment was always looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.53,0:36:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I have to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.59,0:36:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蕾丝安全后  交给她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's for Grace when she's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.94,0:36:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们别无他法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There was no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.47,0:37:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去  哈罗德  我会找到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Keep yourself alive, Harold. I'll be coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.24,0:37:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住我说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Remember what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.37,0:37:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她才是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.18,0:37:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直走  一百步\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Walk a straight line. 100 paces.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.30,0:37:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到达前不许揭眼罩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't take off the blindfold until you're all the way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.87,0:37:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.11,0:38:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快带她离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get her outta here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.34,0:39:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能回到家里肯定感觉很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Day like today, it's gotta feel good to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.04,0:39:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.23,0:39:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Honestly, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.50,0:39:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里会安全吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is it gonna be safe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.01,0:39:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.78,0:39:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们目前得偿所愿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They have what they want for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.56,0:39:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但挡不住他们以后再冲你来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but that won't stop them from coming after you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.08,0:39:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  打开吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Which is why you should open this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.48,0:39:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要的那份在意大利的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That job you were looking at in Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.28,0:39:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被录用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've been selected for the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.88,0:39:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  我都没去面试\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What? I didn't even go on the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.16,0:39:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本应该去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was supposed to leave--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.14,0:39:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的航班\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your flight leaves tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.68,0:39:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作下周开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The job begins next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.95,0:39:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会为你安排好公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They'll set you up with an apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.71,0:39:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薪水  都用护照上的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}stipend, all under the name on that passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.82,0:39:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\b1\c&H111217&\fs10\pos(198.737,187.714)\frz4.417}埃尔斯沃斯\N格蕾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.60,0:39:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱奈尔会护送你安全到机场\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Lionel here will get you to the airport safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.83,0:40:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该重新开始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's a good time to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.28,0:40:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托别回头了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Please don't look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.64,0:40:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Did you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.02,0:40:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.98,0:40:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都是因为他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is he what this was all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.52,0:40:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All I know for sure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.89,0:40:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.65,0:40:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也爱过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and he loved you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.01,0:40:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad1\fn微软雅黑\b1\c&H0703D5&\fs10\4c&HAEAABB&\move(203.549,30.214,143.398,22.5,0,1850)}威胁  清除
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.63,0:40:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Step away from the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.25,0:40:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴在地上  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get on the ground! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.66,0:41:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"的试运行结果  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Results of the Samaritan beta test, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.26,0:41:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名恐怖分子  如你要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}One terrorist, as requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.53,0:41:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的真名\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}His real name
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.40,0:41:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and what he was planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.66,0:41:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不介意了解下详情吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Should you care to know the specifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.78,0:41:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心  我很会处理详情\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Rest assured, I'll get very well acquainted with the specifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.86,0:41:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一切核实\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Assuming everything pans out...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.30,0:41:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持联络\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll be in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.18,0:41:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"就这么失去信号了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So Samaritan's losing the feeds then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.33,0:41:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}For the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.58,0:41:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经取得了参议员的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But we've gained the Senator's confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.75,0:41:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及更宝贵的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And something far more valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.43,0:41:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开车\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Drive.
