Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.00,0:41:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事儿这么重要  得大老远跑来[华盛顿南]芒特弗农\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So what's all the way out in Mount Vernon that's so important?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.23,0:41:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时  这里远离纽约市\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}At the time, it was outside New York city limits
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.96,0:42:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和"撒马利亚人"的视线\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and Samaritan's prying eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.33,0:42:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}At the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.28,0:42:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛失去信号了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima's lost the feeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.75,0:42:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前  只有她在监视了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So for now, the only one watching is her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.04,0:42:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点  孩子们  你们还没出局\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Chin up, kids. You're not out of the game yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.40,0:42:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.06,0:42:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了芬奇  就失去了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We lost Finch, which means we lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.45,0:42:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不尽然\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.84,0:42:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在有"撒马利亚人"七台服务器了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We now have seven of Samaritan's servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.40,0:42:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我所说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.17,0:42:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.37,0:42:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你蒙上了她眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You blindfolded her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.86,0:42:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很承情\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.58,0:42:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举手之劳\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.73,0:42:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你会希望这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Had a feeling you'd prefer it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.55,0:42:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想起步就错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I didn't want to get off on the wrong foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.42,0:43:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.95,0:43:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可太难找了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you've been a very hard man to find.

